    "faq": {
      "title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
      "q1": "What is an 'active conversation'?",
      "a1": "An active conversation is any chat that had at least one message (inbound or outbound) in the last 30 days. Archived or closed conversations don't count.",
      "q2": "Do you charge per WhatsApp message?",
      "a2": "No. We never markup Meta's WhatsApp API pricing. You pay Meta's rates directly. Our subscription only covers the CRM features.",
      "q3": "Can I upgrade or downgrade later?",
      "a3": "Yes! Upgrade anytime, prorated. Downgrade at the end of your billing cycle. No penalties or hidden fees.",
      "q4": "Is there a free trial for paid plans?",
      "a4": "Yes. Every paid plan comes with a 14-day free trial. No credit card required to start.",
      "q5": "How does AI Assist work?",
      "a5": "AI Assist uses GPT-4 to analyze incoming messages and suggest contextual replies. On Free, you get read-only previews. On Starter+, you get real suggestions up to your plan limit.",
